org.conqat.lib.commons.region

Class Region

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.conqat.lib.commons.region.SimpleRegion
      • org.conqat.lib.commons.region.Region
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<SimpleRegion>

    public final class Region
extends SimpleRegion
    Regions represent intervals. Both the start and the end position are considered to be part of the region. Regions can i.e. be used to represent fragments of files.

    This class is immutable.
